      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $\\sum u_n$ une série convergente.\nOn pose $v_n = \\frac{u_n}{1} + \\frac{u_{n-1}}{2} + \\dots + \\frac{u_0}{2^n}$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum u_n\\)</span> une série convergente. On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(v_n = \\frac{u_n}{1} + \\frac{u_{n-1}}{2} + \\dots + \\frac{u_0}{2^n}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9562c497-ec3c-4eea-91e9-9a5932945509",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $v_n \\to 0$ lorsque $n\\to\\infty$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(v_n \\to 0\\)</span> lorsque <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\to\\infty\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ac60816e-e279-47fd-8966-f9306fa2d132",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Césaro.",
        "html": "<p>Césaro.</p>\n"
